{"type":"message","id":"d4fe23ea","parentId":"d63fa7c5","timestamp":"2026-03-18T19:18:26.554Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dzh1bqoh92gm_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\hou-zu\\workspace\\boss-chat-bot\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----         2026/3/19      3:18                data"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":285,"aggregated":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\hou-zu\\workspace\\boss-chat-bot\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----         2026/3/19      3:18                data","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\hou-zu\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773861506551}}
{"type":"message","id":"021ce251","parentId":"d4fe23ea","timestamp":"2026-03-18T19:18:35.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在项目结构已经完整了。让我给用户总结一下实现的内容和如何使用。","thinkingSignature":"e2ab17bc8a25bdeeedfcad302a7622b41167a453079f08dc4a4cf0f1be4fa781"},{"type":"text","text":"项目已完成！我在 workspace 下创建了完整的 **Boss 直聘消息助手**：\n\n## 📁 项目结构\n\n```\nboss-chat-bot/\n├── src/\n│   ├── browser.mjs              # Puppeteer 浏览器控制核心\n│   ├── server.mjs               # API 服务器\n│   ├── handler.mjs             # 消息处理入口\n│   ├── openclaw-integration.mjs # OpenClaw 集成\n│   ├── feishu-integration.mjs  # 飞书集成\n│   └── login.mjs                # 登录脚本\n├── data/                        # Cookie 存储\n├── package.json\n├── README.md\n└── SKILL.md\n```\n\n## 🔄 工作流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐     HTTP      ┌─────────────────┐\n│  Boss 直聘网页   │ ◄──────────► │  Puppeteer 脚本  │\n└─────────────────┘              └────────┬────────┘\n                                          │ API\n                                          ▼\n                                 ┌─────────────────┐\n                                 │   API 服务      │\n                                 │ :3000           │\n                                 └────────┬────────┘\n                                          │\n                                          ▼\n                                 ┌─────────────────┐\n                                 │   OpenClaw      │ ← 你\n                                 │   (AI 回复)     │\n                                 └─────────────────┘\n```\n\n## 🚀 部署步骤\n\n### 1. 安装（服务器上）\n\n```bash\ncd boss-chat-bot\nnpm install\n```\n\n### 2. 登录\n\n```bash\nnpm run login\n```\n\n会弹出浏览器，扫码登录 Boss 直聘。\n\n### 3. 启动服务\n\n```bash\nnpm start\n```\n\n服务运行在 `http://localhost:3000`\n\n### 4. 在 OpenClaw 中使用\n\n你可以直接通过对话发送：\n- **\"查看消息\"** - 查看未读列表\n- **\"查看和 XXX 的聊天\"** - 查看聊天记录\n- **\"回复这个\"** - 让 AI 自动生成回复\n\n---\n\n**注意**: 目前我在本地环境，无法真正连接 Boss 直聘测试。你需要把整个 `boss-chat-bot` 文件夹部署到你的服务器上运行。\n\n需要我帮你做进一步调整吗？比如：\n1. 接入飞书机器人消息（你在飞书发消息控制）\n2. 改成定时自动检查并回复\n3. 其他需求"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":48037,"output":505,"cacheRead":35825,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84367,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773861506555}}
